title: SPY Bias Snow Goggle - Babes need goggles too
description:
SPY Bias Snow Goggle - Babes need goggles too

- Optics by Carl Zeiss Vision
- Flexible polyurethane frame designed for smaller faces Patented Scoop® ventilation system
- 6-Base ARC® spherical dual lens w/ anti-fog & anti-scratch protection
- Triple Layer Isotron™ face foam featuring moisture-wicking Dri-Force™ fleece - Pivoting strap-clip system ensures a comfortable fit, with or without a helmet
- Dual-adjustment, silicone-ribbed strap w/ quick-release buckle
- 100% UV protection
